Image title

Republic of Greece Ambassador to the US, The Honorable Alexandros Philon (background left) and Republic of Greece, Minister of Foreign Affairs, Yeoryios Papandreou meet with US Deputy Secretary of Defense, The Honorable Paul Wolfowitz (foreground), during a defense meeting held at the Pentagon in Washington, District of Columbia (DC).
